                "My usually aloof Persian cat, Princess Luna, went absolutely wild for the Feather Frenzy toy! She's playful again after years of mellowing out. Worth every penny!"
              </blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Review Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-[#00D4AA] transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="p-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF9500] to-[#00D4AA]">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
